#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management/project_templates.rst:98
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Settings` tab, tick the :guilabel:`Billable` checkbox, "
"and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"انقر على تبويب :guilabel:`الإعدادات`، وحدد خانة الاختيار :guilabel:`قابل "
"للفوترة`، ثم انقر على :guilabel:`حفظ`."

#: ../../content/applications/services/project/project_management/project_templates.rst:101
